metadata.description:
Acrylic semi abstract painting.
I use high quality acrylic paints from Royal Talens 
(Amsterdam Expert).

With the NFT, the original owner ( First Owner ) has the right to redeem a physical 36x48" (90x120cm). Original of this work. After purchase please send me an e-mail : motuncay@outlook.com The shipping is included in the price all over the world. (the frame is not included).

Please redeem your work in 3 weeks after purschase done.

Paschamo ( mo tuncay )
